title: 290: Draft trades we would love to see, favorite player by round
itunes:title: 290: Draft trades we would love to see, favorite player by round
description:
Former wideouts Bucky Brooks and Rhett Lewis break down the incoming receiver class (5:38). The guys also give you trades they would love to see (21:48), pick prospects that could sneak into the first round (25:43), as well as their favorite player by round (32:04).
